PrecisAmendments to the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES which revise Articles 4.09 (Performance of Judicial Duties at Courts Martial), 9.04 (Training and Military Duty) and 111.051 (Procedure for Appointment of President and Members), and also enact a NEW ARTICLE: "4.091 (Limitations on Powers and Jurisdiction of the Chief Military Trial Judge)".
